            <title>The Recipes</title>
         </titleStmt>
         <publicationStmt>
            <p>Some recipes. They include some types of bread and a cake. Probably from some kind of bakery recipe book.</p>
         </publicationStmt>
         <sourceDesc>
            <p>A paper page given as testing material for a workshop exercise.</p>
         </sourceDesc>
      </fileDesc>
